summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 TOYOTA SIENNA. THE CONTACT STATED WHENEVER ACCESSING THE REAR LIFTGATE DOOR IT WOULD ABRUPTLY CLOSE. THE CONTACT SUFFERED FROM BRUISES TO THE RIGHT ARM AS A RESULT OF THE FAILURE. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE DEFECT. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 31,000.
